{"word":"G1371 - διχοτομέω - dichotoméō - dee-khot-om-eh'-o - Cut asunder","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διχοτομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dichotoméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-khot-om-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cut asunder</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துண்டுகளாக வெட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to cut into two parts"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1364 - δίς - dís - dece/1364\">G1364</a> and a derivative of <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>temno&#x0304;</b> (to <i>cut</i>); to <i>bisect</i>, that is, (by extension) to <i>flog</i> severely: - cut asunder (in sunder).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}